{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The open source LLVM compiler included with Xcode has evolved at a staggering pace, providing a remarkable combination of lightning-fast compile times and faster code. Explore the power of LLVM’s library architecture, see how Xcode employs the Clang front-end for detailed code analysis, and learn about the latest advancements in C++ support."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/313\/"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-313-LLVM-Technologies-in-Depth"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-313-llvm-technologies-in-depth"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","title":"LLVM Technologies in Depth","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC10"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC10":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","title":"WWDC10","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10","abstract":[{"type":"te